This is a small rush map i created. The layout I had already released as: fy_kristallrush. But the textures were ugly and there were no lighting. 

So I put new textrues into the map and lighting. 

The following weapons are in the map: deagle, m4, ak, para, m3, tmp, p90 and scout. Also there is one galil and one Famas.

there are no buyzones included, nobody has kevlar.

This map is a lot of Fun, you have to try it!
Feel free to download :)
